messages.messageBody:
I read recently that Wagner went to see the Barber of Seville, and told a
friend 'How I love Rossini! But don't tell my Wagnerians - they would never
forgive me!'


>
> ``Wagner's music has beautiful moments but some bad quarters of an hour.``
>
> --Rossini

-Roxana
